txt.en: The spiders of Lhingris have come to the rear gate of Durthang and have now set siege to the fortress in defiance of Ugrukhôr.
Defeated spiders at the gates of Durthang in Lhingris ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
You have defeated many of the spiders setting siege to Durthang in Lhingris and prevented them from spilling forth into Udûn.
You have defeated many spiders at the gates of Durthang in Lhingris.
Spiders can be found near the gates of Durthang in Lhingris.\n\nYou have encountered numerous spiders setting siege to Durthang in Lhingris and should defeat them.

As you feared, many spiders have come to the gates of Durthang in Lhingris. If they are able to breach the fortress, it is likely their numbers shall spill forth into Udûn and threaten the forces of the Free Peoples in Mordor.\n\nYou should defeat as many spiders as you can.
